title: Florø TIF
text:
Florø TIF (Florø Turn og Idrettsforening) is a sports club from the town of <a href="Flor%C3%B8">Florø</a> in the <a href="List%20of%20municipalities%20of%20Norway">municipality</a> of <a href="Kinn">Kinn</a>, <a href="Vestland">Vestland</a>, <a href="Norway">Norway</a>. It was founded in 1893. It has sections for <a href="Sport%20of%20athletics">athletics</a>, <a href="gymnastics">gymnastics</a>, <a href="judo">judo</a>, <a href="powerlifting">powerlifting</a>, <a href="kickboxing">kickboxing</a>, <a href="orienteering">orienteering</a>, <a href="volleyball">volleyball</a> and <a href="table%20tennis">table tennis</a>.
The athletics section uses <a href="Flor%C3%B8%20Stadion">Florø Stadion</a> as their home field.
